# Built oracle binaries — produced by build.sh, `go build`, or
# `go test -c`. Each contributor builds locally; we don't ship
# pre-built binaries. The Rust harness's subprocess invocation
# expects `./bbolt-oracle` (see build.sh). `bbolt` / `bbolt.test`
# cover the default `go build` / `go test -c` artifact names that
# derive from the module basename.
/bbolt-oracle
/bbolt-oracle.exe
/bbolt
/bbolt.exe
/bbolt.test

# Transient test artifacts. Go test drops temp .db files when the
# test writes them to the working dir (we write to TempDir, but
# guard against accidents).
*.db

# Coverage / profiling — may appear during local dev, not shipped.
*.out
*.prof
